Google Translation module

THE IDEA:
Simply connects to Google, translates your pages, show them to the user.
No single mention of Google.

TESTED:
Tested on PHP4 and PHP5.
Doesn't work with anything that Google Translate can't reach.


INSTALL:
After enabling the module, go to settings and 
make sure you have selected your site language.
Then enable the Change language block, you're done.

FEATURE REQUESTS:
Feature requests and feedback is welcome.

Omar Abdel-Wahab
